Story :

Ake, Whan, Don, and Moe are high-schoolboys who always misbehave and never focus on school. But, when the entrance exams is coming, all of them want to pass it in a special way. They visit a holy banyan tree and pray for themselves to easily pass the exams. Soon, their wish is granted. They come back to the holy banyan tree to redeem their vow, but they only find out that the holy banyan tree is now cut off and is transferred into toothpicks! The foursome is now struggling to collect every pieces of the tree before their fortune turns worst.
